## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **climate-adapted medicine 의 의의** = full PLANETARY-HEALTH axis REJECT 후 (axis_expansion_decision_2026_05_08) drug discovery scope 만 narrow 한 disease-orthogonal entry. AMR/policy/surveillance 명시 제외 = scope discipline 의 결과. planetary health 의 모호성 (population health + climate policy + carbon footprint + AMR stewardship + epidemiology surveillance 모두 포함하는 광범위 개념) 을 narrow 한 결과 = drug + microbiome 만.
2. **Rebyota 2022 + Vowst 2023 microbiome paradigm** = first FDA FMT (Rebyota rectal 2022 Ferring) + first FDA oral FMT (Vowst SER-109 2023 Seres). recurrent C. difficile narrow indication. paradigm-defining = "live biotherapeutic product" (LBP) FDA 신규 category.
3. **VE303 Vedanta 8-strain bacterial consortium Phase 3** = defined consortium (vs Rebyota/Vowst undefined-or-spore) — 정의된 8 strain 만으로 C. difficile recurrence 방지. defined-vs-undefined consortium 임상 비교 paradigm.
4. **SYNB1934 + SYNB8802 engineered bacteria** = Synthetic Biologics PKU phenylalanine ammonia lyase (Phase 2) + hyperoxaluria oxalate decarboxylase (Phase 1/2). engineered E. coli Nissle chassis. 약물이 아닌 살아있는 engineered organism = FDA 규제 신규 paradigm.
5. **heat-stable formulation 의 cold-chain disruption importance** = 기후변화 + 전력망 disruption + 분쟁 + 난민 → cold-chain failure → 인슐린 + 백신 활성 손실. heat-stable insulin analog + thermostable rotavirus/measles vaccine = research-only 단계지만 climate refugia 시대 critical. WEAVE scaffold + NANOBOT lyophilized 가 직접 fit.
6. **Valley fever (coccidioidomycosis) climate range expansion** = California/Arizona endemic 이 climate change 로 범위 확대. fluconazole + posaconazole + isavuconazonium azole 약리 1차. CYP51 azole 결합 VQE = quantum-fit primary.
7. **한국 미세먼지 + 황사** = PM2.5 + 황사 (Asian dust) — wildfire smoke 와 다른 source 지만 lung inflammation pathway 동일. ICS budesonide + LABA salmeterol/formoterol + SABA albuterol = 1차. 식약처 framework = 미세먼지-asthma 적응증 expand 가능.
8. **식약처 framework + Korea climate** = 한국 식약처 (MFDS) = climate-adapted medicine 명시 framework 미정착. K-PMA + K-medical 식약처 = drug discovery scope 만 다룸. K-pharma 가 microbiome (CJ Bioscience + KoBioLabs) 진출 — Vowst SER-109 paradigm 추격 가능 (cross-link disease_k_pharma_industry).
9. **scope discipline (AMR/policy/surveillance 명시 제외, drug discovery + microbiome modality 만 cover)** = full PLANETARY-HEALTH axis REJECT 의 명시적 결과. axis-level 은 200 disease budget 외 + scope 모호 + falsifier 제한 → REJECT. disease-orthogonal subset 만 admit = scope discipline = hexa-bio 의 5 axis 보존 + 200 disease budget 보존.
10. **planetary health 의 모호성을 narrow 한 결과** = 본 entry = drug discovery + microbiome + heat-stable formulation + climate-driven infectious disease range expansion 만. wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음 — quantum-only in-silico, microbiome 임상 의미 = Rebyota/Vowst 2022/2023 narrow indication + VE303 Phase 3 + SYNB1934/SYNB8802 Phase 1-2 + heat-stable insulin/vaccine research-only + Valley fever azole mature + 미세먼지 ICS+LABA mature + cholera Dukoral + typhoid Vivotif + antimalarial classical + Dengvaxia/Qdenga 2019/2022.

